<section xml:id="section-fraction-arithmetic">
  <title>Fraction Arithmetic</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      Fractions are numbers. Just like other types of numbers, they can be added, subtracted,
      multiplied, and divided. Doing this arithmetic does not always feel straightforward though, and
      practicing these skills will server you will in an algebra context.
    </p>
  </introduction>

